OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and patchy rain clearing
OL,6,Faway east this morning. Otherwise it
OL,7,Fwill be a dry day with some bright or
OL,8,Fsunny intervals, best of the sunshine
OL,9,Fin the east. Warm across eastern
OL,10,FAberdeenshire.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly dry this evening, just
OL,13,Fthe odd shower around. Then the rest
OL,14,Fof the night will be dry with variable
OL,15,Fcloud and some lengthy clear periods.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FMany places will be dry with
OL,18,Fsome bright or sunny intervals, the
OL,19,Fodd shower across the Cairngorms. Warm
OL,20,Fin the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
