OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FPatchy
OL,6,Frain on Tuesday morning, a few showers
OL,7,Fin the afternoon. Mostly dry on
OL,8,FWednesday, the odd afternoon shower.
OL,9,FEarly rain on Thursday followed by a
OL,10,Ffew showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
